<br />

<br />
With decent monks pulling you won't have any problems getting to the end, but the bosses that spawn are tough, there are 3 of them and have guards, plus they are on timers so you have only one chance to kill them.  You need some 10k hit point tanks if doing this with 3 groups.
<br />

<br />
We failed twice on the bosses, but I want to try again.  Elementals are such a bore.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
