				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">LDoN Raids suck. 
<br />

<br />
Period. 
<br />

<br />
They are three hours of mind-numbing trash to get some generally crappy pieces for the level of effort put in. You really need very close to the full raid allowed at the levels "recommended." 
<br />

<br />
Even when people had nothing to do other than wait a week for Time, these were wildly unpopular. With GoD and OoW out there, I can see just aboout no reason to put a guild through the torture.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.sovereignguild.org/forum/viewtopic.php?t=4429" target="_blank" class="postlink">Master Elementalist Itchyban of Veeshan</a>
<br />
"Nothing to see here. Move along. Move along." 
<br />
"These are not the droids you are looking for."</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
